### Component: API Route Handlers (`/src/core/operator/routes/`)
We will separate route matching and request parsing logic into modular routers sub-delegated by Node's URL dispatcher.

#### [NEW] [telemetry-router.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/operator/routes/telemetry-router.ts)
*   **Role**: Registers REST endpoints for `GET /api/v1/telemetry/summary`, `GET /api/v1/telemetry/slo`, and trace diagnostics.
*   *Size Target*: ~30 KiB.

#### [NEW] [chat-router.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/operator/routes/chat-router.ts)
*   **Role**: Registers REST endpoints for sessions history, completion requests, and agent executions.
*   *Size Target*: ~40 KiB.

#### [NEW] [packages-router.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/operator/routes/packages-router.ts)
*   **Role**: Handles package CRUD, state timeline logs, and download exports.
*   *Size Target*: ~35 KiB.

#### [NEW] [system-router.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/operator/routes/system-router.ts)
*   **Role**: Manages default landing templates (dashboard, wizard), health probes, settings management, and physician doctors endpoints.
*   *Size Target*: ~30 KiB.

