### Component: Core Controller Shell
#### [MODIFY] [dashboard-service.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/operator/dashboard-service.ts)
*   **Role**: Shrunk from 528 KiB to ~60 KiB. Acts exclusively as the lightweight server shell. It initializes the `http/https` listener, wires up the WebSocket server for real-time terminal and log feeds, applies the `AuthGate` and `RateLimiter` middlewares, and forwards all REST traffic to the new `Router` pipeline.

